Step 1:
Create a folder, put both your video and script inside of it.
Step 2:
Go into the folder if not already in it.
Step 3: 
Right click on a clear area in the folder, in the right click menu click "Open in Terminal"
Step 4:
Drag and drop the script into the terminal, press enter. 
Step5 5:
Go into the new folder called transcoded and wait until procces is complete then take your now converted file out of the folder and use it for whatever project you want :D !!!!
